pointer]:\n                - /url: http://xueqiu.com/about/mobile-xueqiu\n            - text: ·\n            - generic [ref=e102]: 安徽\n          - generic [ref=e103] [cursor=pointer]: 关注\n        - article [ref=e104]:\n          - heading [level=1]\n          - generic [ref=e105]:\n            - text: 伊朗若被打服\n            - generic [ref=e107]: ，\n            - text: 石油美元将锁死全球\n            - generic [ref=e108]: ！\n            - text: 这才是美以动武的终极底牌\n            - text: 别被“反恐”“核问题”骗了\n            - generic [ref=e110]: ，\n            - text: 美以联手锤伊朗\n            - generic [ref=e112]: ，\n            - text: 核心就一个\n            - generic [ref=e113]: ：\n            - text: 掐住中东石油的“咽喉”\n            - generic [ref=e114]: 。\n            - text: 伊朗一倒\n            - generic [ref=e116]: ，\n            - text: 美国将彻底掌控全球石油定价权\n            - generic [ref=e118]: ，\n            - text: 石油美元体系再无挑战者\n            - generic [ref=e119]: 。\n            - text: 伊朗是欧佩克第三大产油国\n            - generic [ref=e121]: ，\n            - text: 更扼守着霍尔木兹海峡\n            - generic [ref=e122]: ——\n            - text: 全球20%的石油运输必经此地\n            - generic [ref=e124]: 。\n            - text: 一旦被美国驯服\n            - generic [ref=e126]: ，\n            - text: 不仅伊朗的原油会被纳入美系体系\n            - generic [ref=e128]: ，\n            - text: 沙特\n            - generic [ref=e130]: 、\n            - text: 伊拉克等产油国也将彻底噤声\n            - generic [ref=e131]: 。\n            - text: 到那时\n            - generic [ref=e133]: ，\n            - text: 美国想让油价涨就涨\n            - generic [ref=e135]: 、\n            - text: 想让谁买就谁买\n            - generic [ref=e137]: ，\n            - text: 人民币结算石油的进程将被一刀切断\n            - generic [ref=e138]: 。\n            - text: 对我们而言\n            - generic [ref=e140]: ，\n            - text: 这不是遥远的地缘博弈\n            - generic [ref=e142]: ，\n            - text: 而是实打实的通胀压力与能源安全挑战\n            - generic [ref=e144]: 。\n            - text: A股的油气\n            - generic [ref=e145]: 、\n            - text: 油运\n            - generic [ref=e147]: 、\n            - text: 黄金会被地缘溢价推上天\n            - generic [ref=e149]: ，\n            - text: 但制造业\n            - generic [ref=e151]: 、\n            - text: 消费股将直面成本暴击\n            - generic [ref=e152]: 。\n            - text: 你觉得伊朗会低头吗\n            - generic [ref=e153]: ？\n            - text: 若石油美元彻底锁死\n            - generic [ref=e155]: ，\n            - text: 我们的投资与生活该如何应对\n            - generic [ref=e156]: ？\n            - link \"$中国石油(SH601857)$\" [ref=e157] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://xueqiu.com/S/SH601857\n            - link \"$上证指数(SH000001)$\" [ref=e158] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://xueqiu.com/S/SH000001\n        - paragraph [ref=e159]: 风险提示：用户发表的所有文章仅代表个人观点，与雪球的立场无关。投资决策需建立在独立思考之上。\n        - generic [ref=e162]:\n          - generic [ref=e163] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e164]: \n            - generic [ref=e166]: \"291\"\n          - generic [ref=e167] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e168]: \n            - generic [ref=e170]: \"87\"\n          - generic [ref=e171] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - generic [ref=e172]: \n            - generic [ref=e174]: 打赏作者\n        - generic [ref=e176]:\n          - img \"微信分享\" [ref=e180] [cursor=pointer]\n          - generic [ref=e181]:\n            - link \" 6\" [ref=e182] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: \"#\"\n              - generic [ref=e183]: \n              - paragraph [ref=e184]: \"6\"\n            - link \" 464\" [ref=e185] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: \"#\"\n              - generic [ref=e186]: \n              - paragraph [ref=e187]: \"464\"\n          - link \"投诉\" [ref=e190] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: \"\"\n            - paragraph [ref=e191]: 投诉\n        - generic [ref=e193]:\n          - generic [ref=e194]:\n            - img [ref=e195]\n            - generic [ref=e196]:\n              - generic [ref=e197]:\n                - generic [ref=e198]: 回复@朱雀涅槃\n                - textbox [ref=e