   - link [ref=e271] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /3363958229\n                    - img [ref=e272]\n                  - generic [ref=e273]:\n                    - generic [ref=e274]:\n                      - link \"深秋落叶铺满路\" [ref=e275] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: /3363958229\n                      - generic [ref=e276]: 03-01 13:01 · 上海\n                    - paragraph [ref=e277]: 海湾战争时阴谋论，石油美元说盛行，现在一看伊拉克石油合作方中国成了第一外资合作方，美国退出了伊拉克石油产业。是不是很可笑？\n                    - generic [ref=e279]:\n                      - img [ref=e280]\n                      - paragraph [ref=e281]: 3位达人赞过\n                - blockquote [ref=e282]:\n                  - generic [ref=e283]:\n                    - link \"三板两板2号\" [ref=e284] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: /6233808305\n                    - text: ：伊拉克的石油都是进美元体系的……强制用美国监管的美国金融体系的账户\n                  - generic [ref=e285]: 查看3条回复\n                - generic [ref=e286]:\n                  - link \"3\" [ref=e287] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: \"\"\n                  - link \"88\" [ref=e288] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: \"\"\n              - generic [ref=e289]:\n                - generic [ref=e290]:\n                  - link [ref=e291] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /1812779898\n                    - img [ref=e292]\n                  - generic [ref=e293]:\n                    - generic [ref=e294]:\n                      - link \"单纯的财经小啄木鸟\" [ref=e295] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: /1812779898\n                      - generic [ref=e296]: 03-01 09:22 · 山东\n                    - paragraph [ref=e297]: 某大一直想要通胀，结果来了输入性通胀，哈哈哈哈\n                - blockquote [ref=e298]:\n                  - generic [ref=e299]:\n                    - link \"取经僧\" [ref=e300] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: /5130010169\n                    - text: ：形势严峻，老百姓要倒霉了。就怕资本市场要重新评估经济复苏的预期，重新评估企业出海的预期。我拍脑袋一下，短期对出海企业，比如电网设备、新能源企业、周期反转的化工行业都是利空。对国产替代，自主可控的科技股是利好。估计货币政策财政政策进一步宽松，对地产行业是利好。\n                  - generic [ref=e301]: 查看6条回复\n                - generic [ref=e302]:\n                  - link \"6\" [ref=e303] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: \"\"\n                  - link \"46\" [ref=e304] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: \"\"\n              - generic [ref=e305]:\n                - generic [ref=e306]:\n                  - link [ref=e307] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /1002568185\n                    - img [ref=e308]\n                  - generic [ref=e309]:\n                    - generic [ref=e310]:\n                      - link \"寻常巷陌168\" [ref=e311] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: /1002568185\n                      - generic [ref=e312]: 03-01 09:04 · 广东\n                    - paragraph [ref=e313]: 用点脑子，美国最不希望石油涨价，它要压通胀要降息要缩减不可为继的债务压力\n                - blockquote [ref=e314]:\n                  - generic [ref=e315]:\n                    - link \"好久没吃肉了\" [ref=e316] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: /8158492770\n                    - text: ：通胀是最有效的稀释债务的方式\n                  - generic [ref=e317]: 查看20条回复\n                - generic [ref=e318]:\n                  - link \"20\" [ref=e319] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: \"\"\n                  - link \"42\" [ref=e320] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: \"\"\n              - generic [ref=e321]:\n                - generic [ref=e322]:\n                  - link [ref=e323] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /3123437153\n                    - img [ref=e324]\n                  - generic [ref=e325]:\n                    - generic [ref=e326]:\n                      - link \"慈善的赚钱小熔岩\" [ref=e327] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: /3123437153\n                      - generic [ref=e328]: 03-01 11:02 · 安徽\n                    - paragraph [ref=e329]:\n                      - text: 如果伊朗亲美政权上台，直接的：没了便宜油，巨额投资打水漂。间接的：一带一路